prompts.frontCover: A whimsical, cartoon-style chubby unicorn with a rainbow mane is comically stuck halfway through a giant, frosted birthday donut that is floating in a dreamy, pastel pink and lavender sky. The unicorn has a surprised and slightly sheepish expression, with sprinkles stuck to its nose. Around the donut-unicorn duo, tiny, glowing fairy-bunnies with translucent wings flit about, leaving sparkling trails of light. The background features soft, fluffy clouds shaped like cupcakes and ice cream cones, and a gentle waterfall of liquid starlight cascades down one side of the scene. In the center of the card, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Hope your birthday is as magical as getting the last donut!" The overall style is flat 2D dreamy fantasy anime, with a soft pastel color palette and an enchanting, magical atmosphere.
